---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="FAQ - SnapNotes">
    <main class="mt-14 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="bg-[white] rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">What is SnapNotes?</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700">SnapNotes is a simple, fast, and secure note-taking application that lets you capture your thoughts instantly. Whether you're taking quick notes or writing longer content, SnapNotes makes it easy to create, edit, and organize your notes.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-[white] rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Is SnapNotes free to use?</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Yes! SnapNotes is completely free to use. Create an account and start taking notes right away.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-[white] rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">How secure are my notes?</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Your notes are stored securely in Firebase, and only you can access them through your account. We use modern authentication methods to ensure your data remains private and protected.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-[white] rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Can I access my notes offline?</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Currently, SnapNotes requires an internet connection to create and edit notes. However, we're working on implementing offline capabilities in future updates.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-[white] rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">How do I delete my notes?</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700">You can easily delete any note by clicking the trash icon while viewing it. Don't worry - you'll need to confirm before the note is permanently deleted.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-[white] rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Is there a limit to how many notes I can create?</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700">There's no strict limit on the number of notes you can create. However, we recommend keeping your note count manageable for the best experience.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-[white] rounded-lg shadow-sm p-6">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">How do I get started?</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Simply sign up with your email address, and you'll be ready to create your first note immediately. Click the "New Note" button on your dashboard to begin.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
